author: cmchen
msg: Fixed a bug wherein grayscale pngs were not written correctly.

author: cbartlett
msg: Added isCollapsed() && setCollapsed(boolean) utility methods as per PIVOT-615

author: stsp
msg: (main): Use the SVN_ERR_CL_ARG_PARSING_ERROR error code instead of
SVN_ERR_INCORRECT_PARAMS for consistency with the svn client.

author: stsp
msg: (main): Parse the --listen-port argument with svn_cstring_strtoui64() instead
of atoi(). Make sure the argument parses correctly as a 16 bit unsigned
integer. Previously, any argument was accepted, e.g. --listen-port "abc"
actually worked (PORT ended up being zero, so the OS assigned a random port).
